games.comment: Mike Tolbert, rushed for 82 yards and 2 touchdowns on 16 carries. He would have been the No. 1 waiver-wire pick-up this week had Mathews' injury been serious.    Aside from 2 interceptions,
Mike Tolbert drop in the end zone, but Taylor was able to throw a touchdown on the next play, as Andre Holmes caught a deflected ball.
